            "text": "Importance of Reading Books\n\nReading books is one of the best habits a person can develop.\nBooks are a source of knowledge, imagination, and inspiration.\n\nThey help us improve our vocabulary, thinking skills, and creativity.\nReading also reduces stress and improves focus.\n\nIn today’s digital world, many people prefer phones and social media,\nbut books still provide deep learning and peace of mind.\n\nTherefore, everyone should spend at least a few minutes daily reading books."
